dct_description_sm: Partial cadastral map showing property boundaries, buildings, names of property owners, and radial distances from waterfront.  Relief shown by contours.  In lower left margin: Copyright 1896 by Waldron Bates, Edward L. Rand, and Herbert Jaques.  Oriented with north toward the upper right.  Includes references to points of interest and hotels.
dct_publisher_sm: Geo. W. Stadly and Co. (Boston, Mass), 1896
